Regression Discontinuity Design for Causality Discovery

haiyan yu

1/31/2020

Regression Discontinuity Design

For treatment effect identification of the honorary title in online healthcare communities, This function estimates the standard discontinuity regression:

\[Y=\alpha+\lambda D+\beta_1(X-c)+\beta_2(X-c)+\epsilon\]

packages

}
